YOUR FEEDBACK STATUS HAS BEEN UPDATED
======================================

Hi <%= @user.display_name %>,

We wanted to let you know that the status of your feedback has been updated.

Title: <%= @product_feedback.title %>
Category: <%= @product_feedback.category_display_name %>
Previous Status: <%= ProductFeedback.status_display_name(@old_status) %>
New Status: <%= @product_feedback.status_display_name %>

<% case @product_feedback.status %>
<% when "under_review" %>
Our team is now actively reviewing your feedback. Thank you for helping us improve!
<% when "planned" %>
Great news! Your suggestion has been added to our roadmap. We'll implement this in a future update.
<% when "in_progress" %>
We're actively working on this! Stay tuned for updates.
<% when "completed" %>
Your feedback has been implemented. Thank you for contributing to making our platform better!
<% when "declined" %>
After careful consideration, we've decided not to proceed with this request at this time. We appreciate you taking the time to share your thoughts.
<% end %>

View your feedback: <%= product_feedback_url(@product_feedback) %>

